# 🔧 Wadi Solar Repair Module — Odoo Customization

A custom Odoo module developed for **Al-Wadi Solar Company** to extend 
and enhance the built-in Repair (after-sales) workflow.

## 📋 What This Module Does

- Adds custom fields to repair orders to track solar equipment details
- Extends repair workflow stages to match internal business processes  
- Automates status notifications for repair team and customers
- Integrates with inventory to auto-update spare parts stock on repair completion

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Platform:** Odoo 16/17
- **Language:** Python, XML
- **Database:** PostgreSQL
- **Tools:** Git, VS Code

## 💡 Why I Built This

The default Odoo repair module didn't cover solar equipment-specific 
workflows. This customization reduced manual data entry by ~40% and 
improved repair tracking visibility for the operations team.

